<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="34" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1439,151,898]" pageId="7" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,339,791,817]" pageId="7" pageNumber="34">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name is the feminine form of the Latin adjective stramineous, and refers to its straw­colored body.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
